" class="wp-caption-text"> Walton Goggins as Rick in &#39;The White Lotus&#39; Season 3. CREDT: Home Box Office Inc.</figcaption></figure><p> She also spoke highly of the lengthy monologue on <i>CBS Mornings</i> , and how it relates to the themes of <i>The White Lotus</i> in general, saying that: “I felt like it was what Mike was really trying to talk about for the show.”</p><p> The star explained that if her character Kate and her friends did “what Frank did and been like, &#39;Hey this is what&#39;s happening in my life, I&#39;m having problems in my marriage, I&#39;m drinking too much, I&#39;m doing this, whatever,&#39; they wouldn&#39;t be gossiping about each other because they would immediately put the shield down, they would be vulnerable. And he comes in and he&#39;s like, here&#39;s my truth and he&#39;s unapologetic.” </p><figure id="attachment_3847601" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3847601" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3847601" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/the-white-lotus-kate.jpg" alt="Leslie Bibb as Kate in 'The White Lotus' Season 3. CREDIT: Home Box Office Inc." width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/the-white-lotus-kate.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/the-white-lotus-kate-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/the-white-lotus-kate-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/the-white-lotus-kate-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/the-white-lotus-kate-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/the-white-lotus-kate-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3847601" class="wp-caption-text"> Leslie Bibb as Kate in &#39;The White Lotus&#39; Season 3. CREDIT: Home Box Office Inc.</figcaption></figure><p> Rockwell&#3